                        <interp inst="t18500610-name-158" type="surname" value="BATES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500610-name-158" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BATES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am partner with William Bates and another; we deal</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185006100043"></xptr>
               <p>in cotton. I know these balls of cotton from their appearance only—I do not know Perkins—Atkinson was our warehouseman—I did not authorise him to have these.</p>
